<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <style>
    body { font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif; background: #0a0a0a; color: #e0e0e0; padding: 40px; }
    .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; background: #111; border-radius: 12px; padding: 40px; }
    .logo { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 30px; }
    .logo h1 { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #00d4ff, #7b2fbe); -webkit-background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent; font-size: 28px; }
    h2 { color: #fff; font-size: 22px; }
    .ref { color: #00d4ff; font-family: monospace; font-size: 18px; }
    .detail { padding: 8px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #222; }
    .label { color: #8a8a8a; font-size: 13px; text-transform: uppercase; }
    .value { color: #fff; font-size: 15px; margin-top: 4px; }
    .footer { text-align: center; color: #5c5c5c; font-size: 12px; margin-top: 30px; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="logo"><h1>SAURORAA</h1></div>
    <h2>Booking Request Received</h2>
    <p>Thank you for your interest. Your booking request has been registered.</p>
    <p>Reference: <span class="ref">{{booking.referenceCode}}</span></p>
    <div class="detail">
      <div class="label">Event</div>
      <div class="value">{{booking.eventName}}</div>
    </div>
    <div class="detail">
      <div class="label">Date</div>
      <div class="value">{{booking.eventDate}}</div>
    </div>
    <div class="detail">
      <div class="label">Location</div>
      <div class="value">{{booking.eventCity}}, {{booking.eventCountry}}</div>
    </div>
    <p>Our team will review your request and get back to you shortly.</p>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>&copy; Sauroraa Agency â€” agency.sauroraa.be</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
